[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     20[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     21[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### What's Done Well
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     22[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     23[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - BAA requirement explicitly stated in Setup section ("You'll need a signed BAA because longitudinal treatment data is PHI regardless of de-identification status")
